service.name: Multiple Birth Allowance
service.description: Multiple Birth Allowance (MBA) is payable to customers with three or more FTB children born during the same birth up until they turn 16 years of age. For children aged 16-18 years, MBA is only payable for periods where at least three children of the birth set are full-time secondary students.
